&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sxsw.com/"&gt;&lt;span&gt;South by Southwest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; (SXSW) is one of our favorite events each year. Our team is always inspired by the variety of sessions and discussions with speakers and attendees who are driving change. At this year’s event, the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sxsw.com/conference/tech-industry/"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Tech Track at SXSW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; focused on the balance between the exciting discoveries innovative technology brings with a world that has grown increasingly skeptical of the benefits of the digital revolution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  
